      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s looking flawless and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously loved and kept in tip-top shape, this is the one. Shoot me a message and come take it for a spin before someone else snaps it up!",
