      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, with every service performed strictly on schedule by certified technicians. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster without a single swirl mark or stone chip, while the interior remains in showroom state, featuring supple, uncreased leather and a flawless dashboard. Every electronic component and mechanical system functions perfectly, providing a tight, responsive driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually untouched example of automotive excellence. Included are all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a comprehensive service history binder.",
      "price": 47900.0,
