    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously preserved vehicle, currently maintained in exemplary, showroom-grade condition. This specimen represents the zenith of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards of automotive excellence. For the discerning individual seeking a vehicle of unrivaled pedigree and uncompromising quality, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark. Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance in a vehicle that truly defies its age.",
      "price": 48500.0,
