    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it! It's been my absolute pride and joy, and it's in truly pristine, showroom-level condition. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014not a scratch or a dent in sight, and it still has that brand-new feel every time you get behind the wheel. I'm only letting it go because I'm downsizing, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. It's ready for its next adventure\u2014come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
