    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presented in museum-grade condition, this E30 M3 features the legendary S14 2.3L DOHC inline-four, retaining its factory-spec individual throttle bodies and high-compression piston architecture. The Getrag 265 five-speed dog-leg manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical engagement, feeding power through a 25% locking limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is absolute, with no evidence of subframe fatigue or oxidation. The suspension geometry remains true to its homologation roots, featuring MacPherson struts and semi-trailing arms with uprated Bilstein dampers. Every VIN tag is present, and the top-end was recently refreshed with new valve seals and a precision shim adjustment to ensure optimal reciprocating balance. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector demanding peak mechanical fidelity.",
